snippet.title: The Golf Club VR : Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out some more gameplay, and our new features introduced in The Golf Club VR! 

http://store.steampowered.com/app/489600

http://www.thegolfclubgame.com/
http://www.hb-studios.com

Check out the forums at: http://bit.ly/HB_Forums to keep up with the news and interact with us! Available on October 19th on Steam Early Access for the HTC Vive!
